<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>218</hymn_number>
<author>Kamlala</author>
<title>Van Salem Khawpi</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kapin a tau ngei puou,
 Buoina a zo tau hi;
 Van Salem khawpia,
 Lai tuol lengten;
 $ Gitloh gal a zotau,
 Thihna a lau ta puou,
 Aw, kipakin la a sau (2) D.S.

[V2]
 2. Aw khawvel ka etin,
 Thimin a tuom zing hi;
 Lungkham lusun chate,
 Kapin a mau;
 $ Nau bang I nuihnau le,
 Tuoiin muol a liem hi,
 A w ka gam ding ka ngai hi. (2) D.S.

[V3]
 3. Aw, thisan, na vangin,
 Khawpi tun ka kinem;
 Lui gala lungtuokte,
 Kimna gam nuom;
 $ Aw, ei pui kai in la,
 Angel vamte lakah
 Aw zaila sak ka nuom hi (2) D.S.</lyrics>
</song>